body_html:
What is the code that creates all of the encoder[num] ops? The graph visualizer will automatically group together nodes that are of the form [name]_[num], but these don't have an underscore between name and num.

When using tensorflow to create an op a number of times with the same name for the op each time, tensorflow will automatically add _[num] to each of the created ops after the first one.
